    <item>
      <title>加拿大移民支持率跌至几十年来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/support-for-immigration-in-canada-plunges-to-lowest-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[二十五年来，加拿大人从未对移民水平产生过如此强烈的反对情绪，这个曾经欢迎新移民但却因疫情后大量移民涌入而受到冲击的国家态度发生了转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/support-for-immigration-in-canada-plunges-to-lowest-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 23:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国指控印度政府雇员密谋杀害美国公民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-charges-indian-government-employee-in-plot-to-kill-us-citizen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官指控一名印度政府雇员指挥了一项在纽约暗杀一名拥有美国国籍的锡克教分裂分子的阴谋，但该计划未能成功。此案扰乱了美印关系，与 2023 年在加拿大发生的一起杀人案如出一辙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-charges-indian-government-employee-in-plot-to-kill-us-citizen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 22:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克警告称，哈里斯领导下的特斯拉或将遭遇“疯狂的麦克斯”或“僵尸末日”的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/musk-warns-of-mad-max-or-zombie-apocalypse-fate-under-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克使用了黑暗和险恶的言论，敦促宾夕法尼亚州民众投票给唐纳德·特朗普，试图在这个关键的摇摆州为共和党候选人争取支持者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/musk-warns-of-mad-max-or-zombie-apocalypse-fate-under-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 22:28:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼“总修复者”卸任，普拉博沃接任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/indonesia-looks-to-next-phase-for-nickel-industry-as-fixer-in-chief-bows-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚新总统本周末的就职典礼即将举行，雅加达的政治精英们聚集在新任领导人位于首都郊外的私人牧场，进行最后时刻的讨价还价，以确定未来五年政府的格局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/indonesia-looks-to-next-phase-for-nickel-industry-as-fixer-in-chief-bows-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 22:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克·库班加入哈里斯的行列，就关税问题抨击特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/mark-cuban-joins-harris-on-trail-to-hit-trump-over-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者马克·库班严厉批评共和党人唐纳德·特朗普誓言实施全面关税，称其为“愚蠢”的举动，只会增加已经担心高物价的美国家庭的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/mark-cuban-joins-harris-on-trail-to-hit-trump-over-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 22:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市审计长敦促制定新规则，结束拼车停工现象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/nyc-comptroller-urges-new-rules-to-end-rideshare-driver-lockouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市审计长布拉德·兰德 (Brad Lander) 呼吁修改城市法规，终止应用程序锁定现象，Uber Technologies Inc. 和 Lyft Inc. 曾利用这一做法来违反该市的最低工资法，从而节省了数千万甚至数亿美元的未来司机工资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/nyc-comptroller-urges-new-rules-to-end-rideshare-driver-lockouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 20:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称辛瓦尔之死是结束加沙战争的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/harris-says-sinwar-s-death-offers-opportunity-to-end-gaza-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，以色列击毙哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔有助于结束加沙冲突，这场冲突已导致哈马斯党派分裂，并有可能削弱一些关键选民群体的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/harris-says-sinwar-s-death-offers-opportunity-to-end-gaza-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:28:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在中国，人们普遍认为哈里斯比反复无常的特朗普更受欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/in-china-harris-is-mostly-seen-as-preferred-to-volatile-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国并不迷恋这两位美国总统候选人，但北京方面的谈话表明，与不可预测的唐纳德·特朗普相比，中国明显更喜欢卡玛拉·哈里斯的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/in-china-harris-is-mostly-seen-as-preferred-to-volatile-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉米访华，在敏感时期重振经济关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/lammy-heads-to-beijing-with-uk-still-working-out-china-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·拉米于周五抵达中国，寻求恢复英中关系，尽管北京方面正在台湾周边举行军事演习，且英国政府尚未对双边关系进行审计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/lammy-heads-to-beijing-with-uk-still-working-out-china-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔电力危机重创经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/ecuador-goes-dark-in-a-power-crisis-that-punishes-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[没有电的生活让厄瓜多尔人苦不堪言，他们本已脆弱的经济雪上加霜，也让他们对政治前途产生了担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/ecuador-goes-dark-in-a-power-crisis-that-punishes-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
